<file path="README.md">
# Real Rails – Payments Map FastAPI Backend

## Setup
```bash
pip install -r requirements.txt
uvicorn main:app --reload --port 8000
```

## Endpoints
| Endpoint | Description |
|---|---|
| `GET /api/schemes` | All 27 RTP schemes + global stats |
| `GET /api/schemes/{code}` | Single country (e.g. /api/schemes/IN) |
| `GET /api/timeline` | Schemes grouped by launch year |
| `GET /api/stats` | Aggregate stats for dashboard header |
| `GET /api/download-sample` | 5-record sample for demo download |

## Data Sources
- FedNow (Federal Reserve, USA)
- European Payments Council (SEPA Instant)
- World Bank Payment Systems data
- **Zero Hallucination Policy**: No scheme listed = "Status Unknown"
